          <tr><td>40:00</td><td>12:54</td><td>8:00</td></tr>
        </tbody>
      </table>

      <h3>10K (6.2 Miles)</h3>
      <p>Double the 5K distance, the 10K demands more aerobic endurance while still rewarding speed. Expect your 10K pace to be roughly 15 to 30 seconds per mile slower than your 5K pace.</p>
      <table>
