          <tr><td>80:00</td><td>12:54</td><td>8:00</td></tr>
        </tbody>
      </table>

      <h3>Half Marathon (13.1 Miles)</h3>
      <p>The half marathon has exploded in popularity because it offers a serious endurance challenge without the months of high-mileage training a full marathon demands. Your half marathon pace is typically 20 to 40 seconds per mile slower than your 10K pace.</p>
      <table>
        <thead>
