        </tbody>
      </table>

      <h3>Marathon (26.2 Miles)</h3>
      <p>The marathon is the ultimate test of endurance pacing. Even a few seconds per mile too fast in the early miles can cause a dramatic slowdown &mdash; often called hitting the wall &mdash; after mile 20. Conservative early pacing is critical at this distance.</p>
